{"tid":1985025,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】意大利發起全球50萬聯署，擬向中國索償$8,398億","createTime":"2020-04-23T01:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T02:25:30.000Z","uid":278587,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"06efa2306dc06f1d4c567eb87f6a747378dd7e69","tid":1985025,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200422/large/1587566888_a95b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200422%2Flarge%2F1587566888_a95b.jpg&h=7dde0221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國隱瞞武肺疫情引起全球反制行動，除了美國密蘇里州入稟向中國政府索償，意大利昨日（21日）成立「向中國政府集體訴訟索償」的聯署網站（<a href=\"https://www.covid19classaction.it/）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.covid19classaction.it%2F%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6vxvqPrKL%2FWP0%2BN3ppmbOOw%3D&h=53998a66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.covid19classaction.it/）。</a><br />\n<br />\n意大利通訊社Adnkronos報道，意大利消費者權益保護協會（Codacons）也考慮向中國政府提出訴訟。協會主席里恩兹（Carlo Rienzi）表示，因為意大利的消費者保護法令不完善，他們正與美國律師研究，準備在美國提出集體訴訟，讓全世界都可以參與。<br />\n<br />\n意大利最大商業報《24小時太陽報》（Il sole 24 Ore）報道，意大利北部知名滑雪勝地柯蒂納戴比索（Cortina d'Ampezzo）一間近200年歷史的四星酒店「郵務酒店」（Hotel De La Poste），已向意大利法院提出對中國衞生部門賠償訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n郵務酒店的入稟狀顯示，中國政府延遲向世界衞生組織（WHO）通報疫情，導致意大利北部疫情嚴重，原訂3月在該地舉辦的高山滑雪世界盃決賽因而取消，酒店訂房原本全滿，但因疫情蒙受巨大損失，中國政府應負起賠償責任。<br />\n<br />\nAdnkronos報道，意大利非營利組織「歐洲一體」（Oneurope）帶頭發起向中國政府索償行動，計劃負責人裴洛尼（Ferdinando Perone）表示，根據國際健康規約，任何國家發生重大流行病疫情，必須在24小時內向世衞通報，中國政府沒做到這點。<br />\n<br />\n意大利向中國索償網站已推出，裴洛尼表示，網站計劃在4、5月收集聯署，6月訴諸法律行動。他預計參與聯署將超過50萬人，向中國索償金額可能超過1,000億歐元（約8,398億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200422/7FI5JFZTTK7ZEC7LHPQHC6AAXU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200422%2F7FI5JFZTTK7ZEC7LHPQHC6AAXU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6vxvqPrKL%2FWP0%2BN3ppmbOOw%3D&h=301e5389\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200422%2F7FI5JFZTTK7ZEC7LHPQHC6AAXU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=8ba22db6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200422/7FI5JFZTTK7ZEC7LHPQHC6AAXU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"56249387f821b5e514fe3459866d2125553ad5c0","tid":1985025,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:06:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"20313a98a400770d7f6ac813638c989a817c7a8f","tid":1985025,"uid":270078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:17:36.000Z","msg":"你條link有少少問題, 去依個<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.covid19classaction.it/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.covid19classaction.it%2F&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6vxvqPrKL%2FWP0%2BN3ppmbOOw%3D&h=1e39c023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.covid19classaction.it/</a>"},{"pid":"d287251dc820b53242ea3ceed89db7859bc8e41f","tid":1985025,"uid":164761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9f0d6a6c983ce0cdef15adcf12b5ae0c6ca901","tid":1985025,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:52:26.000Z","msg":"唔係對中國人最有好感咩<br />\n<br />\n幫推「資訊戰」 有個痴線佬準備好晒中宣部旗下Youtuber嘅report<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1957525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1957525</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5e577e9588eb2fec52380cd264252ceb46b61b8b","ti